                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    jcr:title="Empowering people with supportive benefits"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/title/v2/title"
                                    type="h2"
                                    variant="h"/>
                                <text2
                                    cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1659545835858]"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2024-05-02T12:11:44.460-04:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                    text="&lt;p>It was 2021 when Lisa Moreno found herself unexpectedly thrust into the role of caregiver.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>That year, her mother was diagnosed with pancreatic cancer, a rare form of cancer that affects over 60,000 people annually in the United States.&lt;sup>1&lt;/sup>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>Struggling under the emotional impact of the diagnosis, Lisa found balancing her caregiving responsibilities and her career as a benefits operations manager daunting.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>As an AbbVie employee, however, she found a lifeline with the company’s caregiver leave benefit—one that gave Lisa time off to fully focus on being with her mother during her most vulnerable moments, from doctor's appointments to hospice.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                    textIsRich="true"/>
                            </container4>
                            <quote_copy_copy_copy
                                cq:styleIds="[1000000000040,1000000000000]"
                                jcr:created="{Date}2023-08-25T16:36:55.059-04:00"
                                jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                                jcr:lastModified="{Date}2024-05-06T09:40:59.344-04:00"
                                jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/quote"
                                attributionName="Lisa Moreno"
                                attributionTitle="Benefits Operations Manager, AbbVie  "
                                fileReference="/content/dam/abbvie-com2/images/stories/transforming-cancer-care-from-the-inside-out/Moreno-Lisa-headshot.jpg"
                                quote="I had days of quality time, I can't imagine not having, and it's all thanks to a caregiver leave that I was able to utilize to its fullest."
                                quoteType="regular"
                                textSize="h0"/>
                            <container4_copy
                                cq:styleIds="[1653545825687,1653545847150,1653242825678,1653545835982]"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/container/v2/container">
                                <text2
                                    cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1659545835858]"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2024-05-02T12:11:55.261-04:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                    text="&lt;p>For Lisa, her family and the millions of others affected by cancer each year, AbbVie is on a mission to transform cancer care—and that mission extends beyond the laboratory and providing therapies. It permeates every facet of the company, including the support it offers to its people.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>As a leader in oncology innovation, AbbVie understands that fighting cancer takes more than a treatment plan. It requires a broad support network to address the emotional and day-to-day impact, including at home and in the workplace. With this understanding at the forefront, AbbVie is committed to supporting employees in whatever way is needed, from unique benefits to flexibility to helping navigate this complex journey.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                    textIsRich="true"/>
                            </container4_copy>
