                                <title2
                                    cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1651545824678,1651545825694]"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2024-05-08T10:31:55.564-04:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    jcr:title="A pledge to our people"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/title/v2/title"
                                    type="h2"
                                    variant="h"/>
                                <text2
                                    cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1659545835858]"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2024-05-06T10:12:46.205-04:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                    text="&lt;p>AbbVie shows its commitment to employees by proudly serving as a founding partner of the&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://workingwithcancerpledge.com/&quot;>Working With Cancer Pledge&lt;/a>, a global network of companies committed to abolishing the stigma and insecurity that exists for people with cancer in the workplace. But AbbVie’s commitment isn't just defined by a pledge; it's a foundational part of what AbbVie is, coming alive through&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/content/abbvie-com2/us/en/who-we-are/our-principles.html&quot;>its Principles&lt;/a>, the set of core beliefs that guide how the company operates.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                    textIsRich="true"/>
                            </container4_copy_114543579>
                            <quote_copy_copy
                                cq:styleIds="[1000000000040,1000000000000]"
                                jcr:created="{Date}2023-08-25T16:36:55.059-04:00"
                                jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                                jcr:lastModified="{Date}2025-10-28T11:23:09.244-04:00"
                                jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/quote"
                                attributionName="Demetris (D) Crum"
                                attributionTitle="EVP, Chief Human Resources Officer, AbbVie"
                                fileReference="/content/dam/abbvie-com2/images/stories/transforming-cancer-care-from-the-inside-out/Demetris-Crum-headshot.jpg"
                                quote="Together, we’re fostering an unparalleled culture enriched by the support, understanding and flexibility we provide to those navigating the challenges of cancer."
                                quoteType="regular"
                                textSize="h0"/>
                            <container4_copy_copy
                                cq:styleIds="[1653545825687,1653545847150,1653242825678,1653545835982]"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/container/v2/container">
                                <text2
                                    cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1659545835858]"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2025-10-28T11:23:32.303-04:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                    text="&lt;p>&amp;quot;As a founding member of the Working With Cancer pledge, we’re committed to empowering our people leaders to provide exceptional support to their teams, ensuring they understand and have access to all available benefits,” says Demetris (D) Crum, EVP, Chief Human Resources Officer, AbbVie.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>“Together, we’re fostering an unparalleled culture enriched by the support, understanding and flexibility we provide to those navigating the challenges of cancer.&amp;quot;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>Cancer's impact reverberates far beyond a medical diagnosis: It touches the individuals battling the disease, their families and communities. Recognizing this, AbbVie has listened intently to the needs of its people, conducting focus groups with employees like Lisa touched by cancer—themselves, as a people leader or a caregiver—to understand their challenges and provide benefits with their needs in mind.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>From these focus groups, the company has gained valuable insights into the needs of employees navigating the complexities of cancer. They expressed a need for additional support, spanning from help getting expert medical opinions to flexibility on working arrangements and taking a leave of absence. In response, AbbVie has catered its cancer support benefits to directly address these identified needs and ensure employees receive the assistance they need.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>AbbVie’s robust suite of U.S. benefits, including workplace flexibility, empower its people to prioritize well-being and caregiving responsibilities without compromising their professional endeavors.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                    textIsRich="true"/>
                            </container4_copy_copy>
